overview: Tere Naal Hai Jeena is an Indian short musical drama, directed by Zuber K Khan. It features internet sensation Tamkeen Khan and Zuber K Khan in lead. The music video is the debut of bollywood actor Zuber K Khan as director while Tamkeen Khan launched her music label named Tamkeen Khan & Music with this song.
title: Tere Naal Hai Jeena
